headline: FIS Launches 24/7 AI Assistant to Ease Risk Models Management
summary: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., February 23, 2026--Actuaries spend a substantial amount of their time searching for information buried in technical documentation on risk modeling. Global financial technology leader FIS® is changing that today with the launch of its Insurance Risk Suite AI Assistant, a generative AI tool that instantly answers complex questions about building and maintaining risk models—in any language.
